### 1. Login as Fleet Manager
# @name login
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "fleet@transitops.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Store token
@token = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### 2. Get Dashboard
GET http://localhost:4000/api/analytics/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get KPIs
GET http://localhost:4000/api/analytics/kpis
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Monthly Revenue
GET http://localhost:4000/api/analytics/monthly-revenue
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Top Costliest Vehicles
GET http://localhost:4000/api/analytics/top-costliest-vehicles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Export Vehicles CSV
GET http://localhost:4000/api/analytics/export/vehicles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get Permissions Matrix
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users/permissions-matrix
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
